32bit large mode 8080

User needs to provide set_bank helper


At the moment the assumptions are

- All eq ops are 32bit
- All DE short cut ops the caller has set the bank correctly

We need to add near forms of the EQ helpers (ie the 8080 versions) and spot ops with a left
of LOCAL or ARGUMENT as we know those are near (stack based). That needs the compiler adjusting
to know about this first.

